            <title>[CASSANDRA-10174] Range tombstones through thrift don&apos;t handle static columns probably</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-10174</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When inserting range tombstones through thrift in a &quot;static&quot; compact table, the current code doesn&apos;t properly delete the static components of the table (even when it should).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;To the best of my knowledge, we don&apos;t have a test for this (though in all fairness, range deletions through thrift is a pretty late addition and has little coverage) so the first step will probably be to reproduce.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
